{"tid":59430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男警離婚後仍住紀律部隊宿舍 被補控詐騙罪","createTime":"2016-12-29T15:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T05:46:57.000Z","uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9acdea8b793d7f5276d05c1d9867d49ad2e1e51","tid":59430,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:35:42.000Z","msg":"一名男警務人員，涉嫌離婚後沒有向警隊通報，繼續入住紀律部隊人員宿舍。警方諮詢法律意見後，今日在九龍城區拘捕他，並落案控以一項詐騙罪，下月十二日在西九龍裁判法院應訊。涉案人員已被停職。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，絕不容忍及姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"b248e84bfe377d59001b81b65744b4ee4abf6249","tid":59430,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:37:19.000Z","msg":"犯罪實錄。第689章"},{"pid":"b9a60822255ebf29e90c50614fc4ec036282185c","tid":59430,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:44:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07f2562ae0e1eb5cb3bcec6d035c46fe0502c716","tid":59430,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:48:30.000Z","msg":"當值警+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac36187546aa8d0cd2893340115f76221d6669f","tid":59430,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:49:44.000Z","msg":"警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，絕不容忍及姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n呢句應該係繼&ldquo;而家懷疑你同xx案有關，我而家拘捕你，唔係事必要你講，除非你願意講, 但係你所講嘅句說話，我哋將會用紙同筆記底, 將來可能會作為證供用途.&rdquo;後，警方最常用既句子"},{"pid":"15296f81efeabbbb07d2465af234a54cd4bc5edd","tid":59430,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:53:38.000Z","msg":"咩叫&quot;干犯違法行為&quot;"},{"pid":"eb65a827203539dcf0e696d624ec900fd2b858a8","tid":59430,"uid":57787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當值警+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返宿舍嘅時候應該係休班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e711f0122c799352cb10abfcde5aeb85efdf25","tid":59430,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}